For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Swinub (TCG Pocket).

Swinub has been featured on 14 different cards since it debuted in the Neo Genesis expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Swinub cards are normally Water-type or Fighting-type Basic Pokémon.
